      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SAFELY (2) has been beaten for early speed lately, last time finishing fifth (23.93) in a Maiden H at this track. Should be very hard to beat this time. HARLEY GIRL (8) is still a maiden after eight runs but rarely far away, the latest filling a minor placing when third at Warrnambool. Expected to be in the finish again. WARATAH WHO (4) is on debut and has a tricky draw to overcome. Can measure up. PREPARATION (7) is by Fernando Bale out of Crashed making debut. Start all important and will need some luck getting across from the wide draw. Betting to provide the best guide to her chances.",
